[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering system properties for tests**\n\nI’m thinking about setting a system property in the static initializer of Bc_fipsTest. It could serve as a better central utility since static initializers only run when the class is loaded, but that doesn’t guarantee it'll happen before BC initialization. I wonder if I should create a junit-platform.properties file or configure the system property in build.gradle. It seems we can set a default system property for all tests in Gradle, especially focusing on the BC-FIPS context. What about native test configurations?", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0426bda6d0b044020169f9f4dd4a44819eb5454692830ebcd3\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-fTtGNa9p45zWkhPBtB05nOK5n_0G9RFGDvu7abhanqG4CL6yXtCogN412fvBH_suBCG5cxifKRIUCc-EzOvD8FcloBJ5Ff3x4kwyBf1npH0jA1Drre6de9JwtCEHw-CZRvVFvjDX7Htm5vtkIGrp_EaUuoiLEbUHxixVe98tbfOQjK1PRq7wsu7zJErmF2nDsgyjXuZW56QIfrnyV_csOIG1TJ6VOXVm9VweBNW_CSLkkepA321gzzPvk9yjZTmpL_m2qO9xIHVt6-gVVqLcuRgF2gLIab56mrnN2tidUYZUXEAkLZ3Oepsnbg8dK70kjvniNeYiVgm9s7rv_wUffU4NY5XEMaSii-2uJJy5G2LtJYB3cnQQS-_G2kELe1X_Rxry_JZrV4dLpOJJ5cn3W3eaSvIiu5S-HHAEOgaUYdgdn-IbicLUZx90TSPNwoB-O5zSzlaNgUpBXG6ijfE6N-fLSeA-sthm0H_Vr23Oy9i2IGTz-FnnWFMDqm0qKjxlorTGX8m_ul3t_R0KM874WyCVdvUxtS1b9oJNAsGAIHdPxl_guXyeJjGms9iFQSzuwWNsjozcXlzEBwv7k68hsDusdFHrw7_KQAB2M-iOjRkRXVQTVTsLX8nYb42CD6Z07ktu5T2UghY3OPK5IHpD2AzwdTAoGTPgvfLBd-Rtwp-uCq0DnAbQOuF9eLfmYPifniAWbVN1LQVZfeo6QOMIBVw0roKsANrXqZOjie2Zp4yjw3RSxlyPIy5Qu2VCaK3trooUZKn0PdlUdrUINmAI9UnQZE3PllmpPhEqQGipHII1W9DC7Ne7b7yU0hwGChZVbKAfcMoAh9J-6SEfr9xnvh-LjFlAGUkaz3Gpb77q6WRxPBPTflNYhlkAyNXxIKO49K0sGuY2UXu18jmmqLAfYdlhj17imiZTROk6BSVe8mx4wgc436QtfCTiT0Bak2dPIq-cBq998w75KZMRPPD4S1t1dGJnP2h1vcgUyx2yJ0Y-p8RAuFAEiGtQ1PuahPhNU_577lL3zOVj9LeZAL-yum7qHkuzw4-NfOoXTaD8onGH0LqRQ8LLyJEmlpOWLjZO0jpMuhLAxgyvjINbDu7VUnA7IwXALYfLQ_cyTIzvPyY7nhgTc4Hi0PWQRUck1C_5JGwlZkJoT7r08nv4iFbmwd4gpI